      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section id="services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase"><b>Services</b></h2>
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">.</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
            <i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
            <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
          </span>
          <h4 class="service-heading">Better Customer Service</h4>
          <p class="text-muted">Easy enquiries, logde a complaint and understand the customer history and have it sstored.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
            <i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
            <i class="fas fa-laptop fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
          </span>
          <h4 class="service-heading">Auto Assign Tickets</h4>
          <p class="text-muted"> Once the ticket is created it gets auto-assigned to the respective member</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
            <i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
            <i class="fas fa-lock fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
          </span>
          <h4 class="service-heading">Upload Tickets</h4>
          <p class="text-muted">If a ticket or a complaint is taken down in excel file it can be uploaded using this feature</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase"><b>About</b></h2>
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">How it all started</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
          <ul class="timeline">
            <li>
              <div class="timeline-image">
                <%= image_tag("icon2.jpg", :alt => "feed", :class =>"rounded-circle img-fluid") %>
              </div>
              <div class="timeline-panel">
                <div class="timeline-heading">
                  <h4>2009-2011</h4>
                  <h4 class="subheading">Constant Support</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-body">
                  <p class="text-muted">Data for an organization is important and there are a millions things to be done with it, we thought of helping an organization to work it through.HelpMate is the perfect tool!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-inverted">
              <div class="timeline-image">
               <%= image_tag("icon5.jpg", :alt => "feed", :class =>"rounded-circle img-fluid") %>
              </div>
              <div class="timeline-panel">
                <div class="timeline-heading">
                  <h4>Customer Satisfaction</h4>
                  <h4 class="subheading"></h4>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-body">
                  <p class="text-muted">Its neccessary to keep satisfied, and to do this its neccessary for customer complaints to be resolved on time!Helpmate makes sure thats done</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="timeline-image">
                <%= image_tag("icon4.jpg", :alt => "feed", :class =>"rounded-circle img-fluid") %>
              </div>
              <div class="timeline-panel">
                <div class="timeline-heading">
                  <h4>December 2012</h4>
                  <h4 class="subheading">Transition to Full Service</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-body">
                  <p class="text-muted">Autoescalation makes sure transaction is on point to get the things going smoothly.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-inverted">
              <div class="timeline-image">
                <%= image_tag("icon3.jpg", :alt => "feed", :class =>"rounded-circle img-fluid") %>
              </div>
              <div class="timeline-panel">
                <div class="timeline-heading">
                  <h4>July 2014</h4>
                  <h4 class="subheading">Report Generation</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-body">
                  <p class="text-muted">Generates Report for anaylsis and understanding.Helps be in track!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-inverted">
              <div class="timeline-image">
                <h4>Be Part
                  <br>Of Our
                  <br>Story!</h4>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">Contact Us</h2>
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur.</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
          <form id="contactForm" name="sentMessage" novalidate="novalidate">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="form-group">
                  <input class="form-control" id="name" type="text" placeholder="Your Name *" required="required" data-validation-required-message="Please enter your name.">
                  <p class="help-block text-danger"></p>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <input class="form-control" id="email" type="email" placeholder="Your Email *" required="required" data-validation-required-message="Please enter your email address.">
                  <p class="help-block text-danger"></p>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <input class="form-control" id="phone" type="tel" placeholder="Your Phone *" required="required" data-validation-required-message="Please enter your phone number.">
                  <p class="help-block text-danger"></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="form-group">
                  <textarea class="form-control" id="message" placeholder="Your Message *" required="required" data-validation-required-message="Please enter a message."></textarea>
                  <p class="help-block text-danger"></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="clearfix"></div>
              <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                <div id="success"></div>
                <button id="sendMessageButton" class="btn btn-primary btn-xl text-uppercase" type="submit">Send Message</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
         
        </div>
       
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>

</html>
